c: 12
v: 51
t: "(The king) said (to the ladies): \"What was your affair when you wanted to seduce Yusuf (Joseph) from his (true) self?\" The ladies said: \"Allah save us! We know of no evil against him! The ‘Aziz's wife said: \"Now the truth is clear (to all): It was I who wanted to seduce him from his (true) self: He is surely from those who are (always) true (and noble)"